room_description:
You were able to successfully escape from the kidnapper before he returned. You thought it was all over when you got out. Then one day while you were out walking, you hear a noise and someone grabs you and everything goes black!
You wake up locked in jail cells. You realize that the kidnapper has come back for you to finish what he started.This time, he has brought you to his torture chamber. Can you successfully escape before time runs out and you become his next victim?
